oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Wiley and Gene performances - 1941-05-14 - KOMA
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Various performances by Wiley Walker (performer) and Gene Sullivan (performer), recorded on May 14, 1941 by radio station KOMA (Oklahoma City, Okla.)
